metadata.description:
Hi friends! I’m Parker, aka demotapes. I am a producer and artist based in San Francsico. 

I just released my debut EP, called “with friends”. It was a collection of songs I made with a few of my best friends in music. The process for the EP was pretty simple- I would start a demo idea, send it over to a friend, and we would work on it together. “staywithme” is one of the demos I made for this project, but just couldn’t quite find who I wanted to work on it with. So I wanted to give it to you ❤ 

I'm really excited to be working alongside my friends at Family Affair for this release. More on that soon :)
